verbose_text: These data are in line with previous findings demonstrating that PHD3 elicits apoptotic or antiproliferative signaling independent of p53 through KIF1Bbeta, by modulating EGFR signaling, through acetyl-coA carboxylase 2 or by inducing protein aggregates.
evidence: PHD3 elicits apoptotic or antiproliferative signaling independent of p53
